				<div class="comment-body"><p>Rick:</p>
<p>Explain &#8220;the fix in.&#8221; Are you saying that the Administrators have been ignoring the voters, or that there have been deliberate conspiracies to exclude everyone but five people from each category? If so, show evidence.</p>
<p>The Hugo Awards have an admirably record of openness and transparency in their administration process, and you must substantiate your accusations. The response of, &#8220;I hated all of the finalists personally,&#8221; is not a valid answer to this question.</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=369686#respond' data-commentid="369686" data-postid="2177" data-belowelement="comment-369686" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Kevin'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
