				<div class="comment-body"><p>I&#8217;m so excited for Mr. Antonelli! I met him just today and he was the nicest person I&#8217;ve ever met. A good writer, too. I&#8217;m reading &#8220;Letters from Gardner&#8221; right now and I love it. I haven&#8217;t read the other authors but the other authors have to be just as excellent or better, if possible.</p>
